      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPER FREAKY (2) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and three placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (30.21) when sixth over 515m at this track in a Free For All. Looks suited here and rates on top. PAW CARVER (4) goes very well this course and distance starting eight times for three wins and two minors. In the money last time at this track (29.99) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 1.3 lengths third. Looks a key chance on best figures. PAW ISLA (1) pinged the lids from the low draw and led until late to place (29.94) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 515m. Must be included in calculations. QUINLEE BALE (3) will give backers a sight.",
